used to send us the Desert Evening News every week - a pile of newspapers from the Salt Lake City. So I get touch with the Mormons for quite a number of years in one way or another. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Do you remember your father taking you out or your step-father, by yourself?
