My own father, I can remember him taking me out, yes. Oh yes. Around the - round the streets and so on, for little walks, and - my step-father, I used to go out quite - quite a lot with - with him. Yes, he was quite a nice man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Did you do anything special on Bank Holidays do you remember?
