h
e road, a male or a female, especially a male, you could tell his station - in life by his attire. I mean if it was a high silk hat and a tail which was quite customary well he was somebody wasn't he. And the bowler hat and so on. The straw hat was - was 
something that - covered most - most men during the summer, the boater. I used to make boaters myself. And -
