 hair and whatever it might be in his - wear - his attire, you wouldn't be able to - there was a - there was a tremendous difference then. And - you see at Easter}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid415648\charrsid3227008 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
