e knocker ups - the - as I told you - fasten a - the cotton - to a door knocker one side of the street, fasten it over the other and put it to another knocker you see, then - knock at the door so - the person opened the door and then of course when he shu
t
 the door - then there was no one there, he or she - he'd knock the other one himself. That was done in the day mostly though. Pardon? Oh that was quite a popular game wasn't it. And - and putting something over some sort of brick - so they - a - a piece 
of paper so they could kick the paper as they thought. That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Did you ever go to any sort of music halls or a theatre or cinema?
