\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 You told me about the cinema, were there any theatres or music halls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9069422 GL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Well the theatres weren't - didn't exist then. Not in - not before the first world war to any extent. Luton - 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Luton{\*\xmlclose} theatre had just started to - happen just after the first world war. Cinemas didn't happen at all. There was no cinemas. The - the Langton Shows, 
the magic lantern - what you used to call the magic lantern shows - chiefly - chiefly - to do with the - temperance leagues. Were quite popular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 What did they show?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9069422 GL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Well all sorts of - horrible happenings, men getting drunk and knocking women do
wn and children and all - getting involved in it - oh yes. All done to frighten your lives out - keep you away from drinking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 They were well attended were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9069422 GL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Well that - that was quite - there were quite a few of those. Yes. And there were no
 cinemas. Yes. There was no other entertainments apart from the little - social happenings. With - with the churches or the chapels. Well the churches - having their - having their - juvenile - evenings and so on games, so on, in the - in the juvenile - i
n the - in the parish halls. That's quite popular.
