\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9069422 GL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Well that was a very diffi - pocket money was - you see, the first job I had was one and three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid415648\charrsid3227008  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 pence a week. When I was eight.
