be back into - Northamptonshire and round there - I've some little knowledge - of - Greens Norton - and saw what used to happen in the early days there. I - I - that time used to - be associated with - the Duke of Bedford's - estates, and there was a trem
endous difference I know between that top - those top strata, and - the workers. But - but -
