Well the - he was a shy man, the brother would be more - he was a - a Vauxhall man, Vauxhall then wasn't the Vauxhall now, it was simply an engineering works
 you see, but he would be more - more capable of - because my - my - my father-in-law - couldn't read or write. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 So he'd be shy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9069422 GL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 You had a best man, who was your best man?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9069422 GL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 My best - my best man - was - the - my best man was t
he brother who became - brother of the man who became Mayor of Luton, it's quite the history of this Mayor because he was a cripple - and at the school - collected together and got him a donkey and cart to sell vegetables, and - eventually he became - got
 up and up and he became Mayor of Luton - and he died quite a wealthy man, but - his brother - was my age and - we teamed up, mind you he was - he was then courting the girl next door to my wife. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Were the bride and groom's guests separated in the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9069422 GL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Oh yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Do you know why that happens?
