\insrsid12780690\charrsid3227008 ey}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 s, and that - the taxi took us back to the - the bride's home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Was it decorated?
