\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 It didn't have ribbons on or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9069422 GL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 That could have - that could have happened at different times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 But not with you?
