{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Alice{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, yes, there was a wedding cake, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1203760 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8460570\charrsid3227008 Did you have speeches?
