 and - it rained - when we went - we had a horse conveyance from the station to - our - board residence, yes, that's quite true, yes, I - a horse - conveyance but it was raining - torrents. Didn't mind that you know. There was con - I'm sorry, there was c
o
nfetti. I'll tell you why I - I - why I remember, because the - very small boarding house, very nice little - widow keeping this boarding house and we were the two only people because - they were only used in the middle of the summer - invariably. And - s
h
e'd very very - she'd very very - carefully managed to get - some pieces of confetti, and she put 'em onto the - sort of dressing table of us to see. Knowing that we - knew - well we were - newly married. Oh yes, I remember that so that - yes, we had conf
etti. Yes.
